    {
        "content": "<p>I think I see two fixes:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Force the <code>current-&gt;mm</code> access to happen inside the <code>current!()</code> macro, instead of letting you do it later.</li>\n<li>Have <code>kthread_use_mm</code> require the closure to be <code>Send</code>.</li>\n</ol>",
        "id": 485090039,
